    {
      "id": "mrcghv6akggs1t0i3xi",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 545,
      "y": 878,
      "text": "Zero-shot (tentativa 1):\n\n\"Escreva um parágrafo introdutório sobre\nKubernetes para iniciantes. Tom informal.\"\n\n⚠️ \"Tom informal\" é vago — cada execução\ninterpreta diferente. Resultado imprevisível.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "updated": 1,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "width": 313,
      "height": 113,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
    {
      "id": "mrcghv6yi1qng3qud2",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 530,
      "y": 1015,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 210,
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "strokeColor": "#adb5bd",
      "roughness": 0,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
