    {
      "id": "mrcgicpw36kvsb7u5kh",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1135,
      "y": 830,
      "strokeColor": "#4c6ef5",
      "text": "1. Listar pods — \"Quais pods estão rodando?\"",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "updated": 1,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "width": 383,
      "height": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "mrcgicqkwo2ni7b2hot",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1135,
      "y": 858,
      "text": "\"Liste todos os pods do namespace default\ncom seu status atual.\"\n\n🔧 Tool: MCP Kubernetes -> kubectl get pods\n🧠 Modelo: Organiza, destaca status, traduz\ntermos técnicos (CrashLoopBackOff = \"o pod\nestá reiniciando repetidamente por erro\")\n\n💡 Tool traz dados brutos. Modelo interpreta.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "angle": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "roundness": null,
      "boundElements": null,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "locked": false,
      "seed": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1,
      "updated": 1,
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "width": 306,
      "height": 146,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e"
    },
